1
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:35,040
President Cui told me at the time

2
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:37,280
this notice

3
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:38,720
would be best issued by me.

4
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,600
But the hospital office could issue it too.

5
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:45,200
Besides the Health Commission's investigation notice,

6
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:46,840
our hospital

7
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,840
also needs to issue a disciplinary report

8
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,800
to make the hospital's attitude

9
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:51,480
and position clear.

10
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:54,600
You were Xuemie's attending doctor,

11
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,800
and you lead the congenital heart program.

12
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:59,240
The department director selection

13
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,040
is also underway now.

14
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,240
This report

15
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:04,280
naturally should come from you.

16
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:07,120
But

17
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,480
considering

18
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,880
your relationship with Professor Fang,

19
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,120
the hospital

20
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:12,960
can make other arrangements.

21
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:17,320
I chose to issue it myself.

22
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,200
Why?

23
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,320
You weren't forced?

24
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:29,200
I'm in charge of the congenital heart program.

25
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,240
Of course I should take on

26
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,120
this responsibility.

27
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:33,600
Exactly.

28
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,400
Because you're

29
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:35,640
in charge of the congenital heart program,

30
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,520
you know the whole matter,

31
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,640
inside and out,

32
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:38,800
better than anyone.

33
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:40,560
You were also the one who asked Mom

34
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:41,640
to help perform the surgery.

35
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,440
Then at the review meeting,

36
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,840
you didn't speak up for Mom.

37
00:02:44,920 --> 00:02:45,760
And now you chose

38
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,120
to issue this notice yourself?

39
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:47,800
It was precisely because

40
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,120
I asked Mom to do the surgery.

41
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:50,480
Who in the hospital doesn't know

42
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,520
my relationship with Mom?

43
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:53,520
If I don't make my position clear,

44
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,640
how can I convince anyone?

45
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:55,880
But this punishment

46
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:57,040
is already too harsh.

47
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:58,760
And if the penalty

48
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,880
comes out of your mouth,

49
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:00,520
have you thought about

50
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:01,640
how Mom would feel?

51
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:02,920
Then what do you want me to do?

52
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:04,200
Mom was punished,

53
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,280
so I should be dragged down too?

54
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:07,480
Only then are we a family,

55
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:07,800
is that it?

56
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,640
That's not what I mean.

57
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,960
But at least you could have chosen

58
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,520
not to issue the notice.

59
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,520
I had no choice.

60
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,200
The leaders' intention

61
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:13,920
was already very clear.

62
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,640
They said you had a choice.

63
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,480
She only said that.

64
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,480
That's not what she meant.

65
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,800
Then what did she mean?

66
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:20,840
She meant I should...

67
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:23,600
If I had refused then,

68
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:24,240
I would have withdrawn directly

69
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,400
from the director selection.

70
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,520
Don't you understand?

71
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:29,040
So,

72
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,200
it's really like people are saying?

73
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,520
For the promotion,

74
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:32,880
you can put everything else aside?

75
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:34,200
Yes. That's right.

76
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,200
How did you become like this?

77
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:42,840
Xiaoran.

78
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:44,480
I'm leaving.

79
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:45,840
Xiaofeng.

80
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,240
Sit down and eat.

81
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,320
You did nothing wrong.

82
00:03:53,040 --> 00:03:54,760
I also think

83
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:55,560
you were the right person

84
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,920
to issue the notice.

85
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,200
What's happened has happened.

86
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,560
Who issued it

87
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:05,160
makes no difference to me.

88
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:07,200
It's just that the congenital heart program

89
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,720
still has Phase Two and Phase Three.

90
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,720
If you don't step forward

91
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,280
and let public opinion keep spreading,

92
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,480
once trust is damaged,

93
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:15,800
the patients who come later

94
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,840
may lose their chance

95
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,520
to receive treatment.

96
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:20,840
But I still feel it's unfair to you.

97
00:04:20,840 --> 00:04:22,200
I always thought

98
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,640
my brother was forced.

99
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,320
So at that moment,

100
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,240
would standing by and protecting yourself

101
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:28,840
have been the right thing to do?

102
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:30,040
Everyone acted out of empathy

103
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:31,160
and crossed a serious line together.

104
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,040
But in the end, all the responsibility

105
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,720
fell on you alone.

106
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,640
No one even said a word for you.

107
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,320
Xiaoran.

108
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:40,840
In that surgery,

109
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,800
I was the lead surgeon.

110
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,160
So many experts in the field

111
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:50,840
are my juniors.

112
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,080
The guidelines for fetal intervention

113
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,760
and the expert consensus
were both documents

114
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,880
I helped write.

115
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:58,800
If I have enjoyed that honor,
I must also bear that responsibility,

116
00:04:58,880 --> 00:04:59,440
right?

117
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:01,880
The four of us in this family

118
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:03,320
are all capable of

119
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,200
taking responsibility for our actions.

120
00:05:04,760 --> 00:05:05,720
At that moment,

121
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:08,840
whether to do the surgery or not

122
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:09,840
was my decision.

123
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,040
It had nothing to do with Xiaofeng.

124
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:21,040
Saying that

125
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,480
I took the risk

126
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:23,840
for my son?

127
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:26,040
Is that my style?

128
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,240
I wanted to help Xuemie

129
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:35,040
keep her baby.

130
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,200
That's true.

131
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,520
But

132
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:40,280
besides that,

133
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:42,520
I

134
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:45,240
also had my own ambition.

135
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,040
The first twin fetal intervention

136
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,280
in the country,

137
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,600
with such high difficulty,

138
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,880
using the newest equipment too.

139
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,200
If it had succeeded,

140
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,320
it would've been a milestone

141
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:03,480
for the entire field.

142
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:07,200
That itch to test your skills...

143
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,560
You understand it best, Xiao Lin.

144
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,560
I do.

145
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,160
But I failed.

146
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,720
So I have no objection

147
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,560
to the current handling.

148
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:23,720
Xiaofeng, your position wasn't wrong either.

149
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,720
My only regret

150
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,280
is that I couldn't help Xuemie

151
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,080
keep her child.

152
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,600
Mom.

153
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:32,840
Xuemie said it herself.

154
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:34,760
She knows you all did your best.

155
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:35,960
She did her best too.

156
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:38,040
She has no regrets.

157
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,200
So don't

158
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,160
feel wronged for me anymore.

159
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:44,120
And stop blaming Xiaofeng.

160
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:45,160
What outsiders say about him

161
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,880
doesn't matter.

162
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:49,320
In the future, don't say things

163
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,200
that hurt the family again.

164
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,600
That was also why
I asked you all to dinner.

165
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:55,160
Let's put this matter behind us today.

166
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:57,520
As for me,

167
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,400
I'll take this chance

168
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,640
to take a break for a while.

169
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,320
I'm planning

170
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:12,080
to meet up with Shi Wei

171
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:13,440
and go on a road trip.

172
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:16,880
So suddenly?

173
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:18,200
You're going to Europe?

174
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,640
He happens to have time off.

175
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:20,760
He's back in China.

176
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,120
We've always wanted to go to Xinjiang.

177
00:07:25,640 --> 00:07:27,800
I'm not running away to heal.

178
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,320
Don't look at me like that.

179
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:32,200
Eat, Xiao Lin.

180
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,640
Come on, come on.

181
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:54,600
They're out.

182
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,280
Yes, yes, right here.

183
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:57,840
All right, thank you.

184
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,520
Mom.

185
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,520
I want to go with you.

186
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,040
My little sweetheart

187
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,440
is smothering me.

188
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:08,440
I don't care.

189
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,440
Then we're leaving.

190
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,440
Get some rest.

191
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:14,720
Goodbye, Aunt Fang.

192
00:08:14,840 --> 00:08:15,560
Be careful.

193
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:17,840
Call me when you arrive.

194
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:26,520
How are you getting home?

195
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:28,880
I'll take a taxi.

196
00:08:38,040 --> 00:08:38,920
The stars and the sea

197
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:41,200
come at a price.

198
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:48,960
But the price you paid this time

199
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,720
was too high.

200
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:54,760
What you hurt

201
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:57,840
is something I've longed for

202
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,200
my whole life.

203
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:31,920
Director Zhou.

204
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,320
I'm here to apologize.

205
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:37,280
Director Zhou.

206
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:39,040
I really didn't expect the punishment

207
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:40,200
to be this severe.

208
00:11:43,760 --> 00:11:44,400
Director Zhou,

209
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:45,800
can you hear me out?

210
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:46,840
I really came to apologize.

211
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:47,840
What else is there to say?

212
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:50,600
You're the product representative.

213
00:11:50,640 --> 00:11:51,480
You have your position.

214
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,840
You don't need to explain anything to me.

215
00:11:53,880 --> 00:11:54,600
Director Zhou.

216
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,160
Do you have

217
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:57,200
a big prejudice against me?

218
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,160
Is that prejudice?

219
00:11:58,920 --> 00:12:00,200
Isn't that your usual style?

220
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:02,200
Doing whatever it takes

221
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:03,640
to reach your goal.

222
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:04,480
Whether you pushed Professor Fang that day,

223
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:05,520
you know it yourself.

224
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:06,440
I admit it.

225
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:09,120
I should have stopped her then.

226
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,160
I'm sorry

227
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:11,880
things ended this way.

228
00:12:12,760 --> 00:12:14,320
But I was once a doctor too.

229
00:12:14,760 --> 00:12:16,200
If it had been me that day,

230
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:18,120
I also would have taken the risk to intervene.

231
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,520
Because that was a little life.

232
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:22,440
A life was at stake.

233
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,440
I wanted her to survive.

234
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:25,880
If we could have saved her,

235
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:27,280
I think it would've been worth anything.

236
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,240
Of course, I also admit

237
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:32,840
my motives weren't pure.

238
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,200
Because I'm in sales now.

239
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:36,800
I have my own pressure

240
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,200
and my own helplessness.

241
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:40,200
I also hope, Director Zhou,

242
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:42,640
that you can understand me a little.

243
00:12:44,040 --> 00:12:44,720
What's the point

244
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:45,600
of saying this now?

245
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:47,080
Why didn't you say it

246
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:47,840
at the review meeting that day?

247
00:12:48,520 --> 00:12:49,760
Would it have mattered if I had?

248
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:51,960
Would it have reduced

249
00:12:52,040 --> 00:12:53,200
Professor Fang's punishment?

250
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:57,840
I watched that video.

251
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,040
I don't think you did anything wrong.

252
00:13:01,040 --> 00:13:01,640
You did

253
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:03,080
what you believed was right.

254
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:04,760
I'm the same.

255
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,240
I came today to apologize to you

256
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:08,720
with full sincerity.

257
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:10,840
I want to say sorry

258
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:12,080
to both you and Professor Fang.

259
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,720
I also hope you can forgive me.

260
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,280
You've apologized.

261
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:21,200
You've said your piece.

262
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:22,840
Director Zhou.

263
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:24,640
There's still a long road ahead.

264
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:50,480
Can you do it, Xiao Rui?

265
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:53,560
Don't be so loud.

266
00:13:54,160 --> 00:13:54,920
You'll scare the fish away.

267
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,440
Scare the fish away?

268
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:59,480
Don't blame the fish for being timid.

269
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:00,960
You're just not good enough.

270
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:10,720
I'm going to get some water.

271
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,440
Mom, have you set off?

272
00:14:43,160 --> 00:14:44,120
Aren't you thirsty?

273
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:45,840
You haven't even poured water.

274
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:52,160
Still worried about Aunt Fang?

275
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:54,960
I regret it.

276
00:14:56,160 --> 00:14:57,840
I should have seen her off at the airport.

277
00:14:58,480 --> 00:14:58,960
No need.

278
00:14:59,160 --> 00:14:59,840
Aunt Fang said

279
00:14:59,880 --> 00:15:00,840
we didn't need to.

280
00:15:01,800 --> 00:15:03,200
And I think she's fine.

281
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:04,760
She's actually pretty cool.

282
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:07,520
What she said was right.

283
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:09,240
Doctors treat illness and save lives.

284
00:15:09,920 --> 00:15:10,920
If it works, it works.

285
00:15:11,040 --> 00:15:12,280
If it fails, you accept it and face it.

286
00:15:12,520 --> 00:15:13,200
She's open and upright,

287
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,400
not hesitant at all.

288
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,160
Think about when

289
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,200
I saved Zhang Yuxi.

290
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:18,960
If I hadn't saved her,

291
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:20,840
I would have been punished in the end.

292
00:15:21,760 --> 00:15:23,480
I saved her,

293
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,480
and I was still punished.

294
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:27,200
But I'm still quite worried about her.

295
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:29,200
On the surface,

296
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:30,080
she looks fine.

297
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:31,320
But I think this time

298
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,480
she was really hurt.

299
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:35,480
She and your brother

300
00:15:35,480 --> 00:15:36,600
finally made peace.

301
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:38,560
I really don't want

302
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:40,320
our whole family
to have any knots in our hearts.

303
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:42,840
Knots?

304
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:45,520
Bring the knots to me.

305
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:47,280
I'll cut out any knot.

306
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:48,440
Forget knots.

307
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:49,800
I can even cut out tumors.

308
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:53,880
She's leaving this time

309
00:15:53,880 --> 00:15:55,200
for several months.

310
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:56,960
I'm worried that as time passes,

311
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:58,240
it'll be even harder to untangle.

312
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:03,480
Mom.

313
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:08,800
I still wanted to come see you off.

314
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:11,080
Why didn't you say so earlier?

315
00:16:11,560 --> 00:16:12,520
I've already called a car.

316
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:14,520
If I had, you wouldn't have let me.

317
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:15,560
Cancel it.

318
00:16:47,160 --> 00:16:48,200
Do you have everything?

319
00:16:49,520 --> 00:16:50,720
Xiaoran, you know her.

320
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:53,160
Like a little housekeeper,
worrying over everything.

321
00:16:53,520 --> 00:16:54,320
Last night,

322
00:16:54,520 --> 00:16:55,240
she helped me pack

323
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:56,400
until midnight.

324
00:16:58,120 --> 00:16:58,760
What about cash?

325
00:16:58,800 --> 00:16:59,640
Did you bring some?

326
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:00,400
Some places

327
00:17:00,400 --> 00:17:01,240
don't have mobile payment.

328
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:02,840
I did. Don't worry.

329
00:17:03,520 --> 00:17:04,240
Also, don't make your itinerary

330
00:17:04,280 --> 00:17:05,520
too packed or tiring.

331
00:17:06,080 --> 00:17:06,880
Keep in touch at all times.

332
00:17:07,120 --> 00:17:08,480
When you change locations, let us know you're safe.

333
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:09,960
Why are you nagging

334
00:17:10,040 --> 00:17:11,160
just like Xiaoran?

335
00:17:14,040 --> 00:17:14,800
These two kids.

336
00:17:29,840 --> 00:17:30,480
Mom.

337
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:34,160
I'm sorry.

338
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:36,840
I made you sad.

339
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,840
I've already told you.

340
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:40,120
I understand you.

341
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:41,320
I truly understand you.

342
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:43,080
If it were me,

343
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:44,640
I would make the same choice.

344
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:49,920
The path

345
00:17:51,080 --> 00:17:52,200
you're going to take

346
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:54,200
will bring greater challenges,

347
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,560
more complicated situations,

348
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:56,840
and even costs

349
00:17:56,840 --> 00:17:58,480
you never expected.

350
00:18:01,560 --> 00:18:02,240
I know.

351
00:18:04,280 --> 00:18:05,040
This path

352
00:18:07,080 --> 00:18:08,760
can't be reached

353
00:18:09,320 --> 00:18:10,040
just by being a good person

354
00:18:10,720 --> 00:18:11,720
or a good doctor.

355
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:16,520
You've come this far

356
00:18:17,480 --> 00:18:18,280
all on your own.

357
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:19,880
I believe in you.

358
00:18:20,920 --> 00:18:21,760
And I wish you well.

359
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:29,880
After working for over thirty years,

360
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:31,960
this is the first time

361
00:18:32,520 --> 00:18:34,400
I'm taking such a long break.

362
00:18:37,800 --> 00:18:38,400
It's good.

363
00:18:38,600 --> 00:18:39,400
Go out and look around.

364
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:41,120
Clear your mind.

365
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:43,920
Think about your road ahead.

366
00:18:48,520 --> 00:18:49,560
Six months later, I'll come back strong,

367
00:18:49,560 --> 00:18:50,960
still sharp as ever.

368
00:18:57,520 --> 00:18:58,840
Just have fun.

369
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,160
Get plenty of rest.

370
00:19:05,320 --> 00:19:06,200
As for Xiaoran,

371
00:19:07,480 --> 00:19:08,720
I'll talk to her properly.

372
00:19:22,080 --> 00:19:23,120
Watch the road.

373
00:19:31,080 --> 00:19:33,560
Bye-bye, little fish.

374
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:39,040
Why do you have so few?

375
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:42,480
How is this few?

376
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:44,200
You haven't even seen mine.

377
00:19:45,840 --> 00:19:46,840
Let's go home.

378
00:19:47,840 --> 00:19:48,760
Everyone go.

379
00:19:50,120 --> 00:19:51,200
Have a safe trip.

380
00:19:51,520 --> 00:19:52,520
Come back soon.

381
00:19:56,840 --> 00:19:57,480
He lost.

382
00:19:58,560 --> 00:19:59,520
I did not lose.

383
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:01,040
I caught more varieties.

384
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,440
Mom has boarded.

385
00:20:02,520 --> 00:20:03,200
That fast?

386
00:20:04,120 --> 00:20:05,520
She said my brother saw her off.

387
00:20:06,480 --> 00:20:07,640
See? The knot's untied.

388
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:09,640
What's that saying?

389
00:20:10,200 --> 00:20:12,760
The one who tied the bell is Zhou Xiaofeng.

390
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:15,120
All right, let's go back too.

391
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:15,840
Let's go.

392
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:34,920
Today,

393
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:36,240
