of the Cardiology Department.

403
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:02,200
Starting today,

404
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:03,280
Director Zhou Xiaofeng

405
00:21:03,520 --> 00:21:04,720
will be fully in charge of

406
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,760
the medical work,

407
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:08,240
teaching, research,

408
00:21:08,280 --> 00:21:09,920
and administrative management
of the Cardiology Department.

409
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:17,080
Director Zhou,

410
00:21:17,560 --> 00:21:18,600
Cardiology

411
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:20,720
is one of our hospital's key departments.

412
00:21:21,080 --> 00:21:22,840
You carry great responsibility

413
00:21:23,040 --> 00:21:23,920
and a heavy workload.

414
00:21:24,320 --> 00:21:25,280
You'll have to work hard.

415
00:21:25,640 --> 00:21:27,200
I won't let the leadership's trust down.

416
00:21:27,520 --> 00:21:28,080
Good.

417
00:21:28,080 --> 00:21:28,920
Then congratulations.

418
00:21:29,080 --> 00:21:30,040
Congratulations, Director Zhou.

419
00:21:31,840 --> 00:21:33,120
Why don't you two take a photo together?

420
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:36,160
How old is Director Zhou this year?

421
00:21:37,120 --> 00:21:37,840
Thirty-eight.

422
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:40,240
Then he broke the record

423
00:21:40,320 --> 00:21:41,760
