424
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:44,320
Who held it before?

425
00:21:47,280 --> 00:21:47,960
Me.

426
00:21:50,320 --> 00:21:51,520
Everyone come up.

427
00:21:51,600 --> 00:21:52,760
Let's take

428
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:53,880
