429
00:21:54,080 --> 00:21:54,480
Come on.

430
00:21:54,520 --> 00:21:55,040
Come on.

431
00:21:56,640 --> 00:21:57,200
Come on.

432
00:21:58,520 --> 00:21:59,200
Everyone together.

433
00:21:59,440 --> 00:21:59,880
Come on.

434
00:22:00,080 --> 00:22:00,440
Come on.

435
00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:01,320
Let's take a picture.

436
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:02,520
