437
00:22:04,120 --> 00:22:04,840
Xiaoran.

438
00:22:05,440 --> 00:22:05,920
Dr. Fang.

439
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:06,960
Come on.

440
00:22:07,320 --> 00:22:08,280
Let's take a group photo.

441
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:09,200
Come over.

442
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:10,520
Stand closer together.

443
00:22:11,520 --> 00:22:12,440
Everyone come, come, come.

444
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:14,520
Move toward the center.

445
00:22:15,760 --> 00:22:16,600
You come here.

446
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:17,800
Stand beside your brother.

447
00:22:17,880 --> 00:22:18,760
You, move over there.

448
00:22:19,240 --> 00:22:19,600
Come on.

449
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:20,240
Go, go.

450
00:22:20,520 --> 00:22:21,640
Everyone on this side, move in.

451
00:22:22,280 --> 00:22:23,200
Everyone look at me.

452
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:24,480
When I raise my thumb,

453
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:25,560
