456
00:22:29,080 --> 00:22:29,880
Let's try once.

457
00:22:30,200 --> 00:22:31,320
Heart Center!

458
00:22:31,560 --> 00:22:32,840
Forward!

459
00:22:36,800 --> 00:22:37,520
Good, that's good.

460
00:22:37,600 --> 00:22:38,160
Good.

461
00:22:38,280 --> 00:22:38,840
Thank you.

462
00:22:39,080 --> 00:22:39,800
Director Zhou.

463
00:22:40,120 --> 00:22:41,200
Congratulations.
Congratulations, Director Zhou.

464
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,720
Congratulations, Director Zhou.

465
00:22:49,280 --> 00:22:50,440
Aunt Fang saw it so fast.

466
00:22:51,800 --> 00:22:53,120
Mom has been waiting for it.

467
00:23:12,520 --> 00:23:13,800
Congratulations, Director. Congrats.

468
00:23:13,840 --> 00:23:14,920
Amazing, Director Zhou.

469
00:24:05,880 --> 00:24:07,600
I really didn't expect it to be him.

470
00:24:08,560 --> 00:24:09,280
My guess is

471
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:10,840
