484
00:24:56,320 --> 00:24:57,240
Not just at Dongli.

485
00:24:57,840 --> 00:24:58,920
Among Dongjiang's Grade-A tertiary hospitals,

486
00:24:58,920 --> 00:24:59,520
he's the youngest major department head

487
00:24:59,600 --> 00:25:01,200
in the past decade.

488
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:02,800
Sit down, sit down.

489
00:25:06,720 --> 00:25:08,200
I didn't expect that at a time like this,

490
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:09,480
they still chose him.

491
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:10,520
I thought

492
00:25:10,560 --> 00:25:11,800
