494
00:25:13,560 --> 00:25:14,880
After all, public opinion was bad.

495
00:25:15,520 --> 00:25:16,720
And Fang Zhuqing is his mother.

496
00:25:19,200 --> 00:25:20,080
Here, coffee.

497
00:25:20,440 --> 00:25:20,920
Thanks.

498
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:23,240
Ouyang.

499
00:25:24,120 --> 00:25:24,840
Are you still

500
00:25:24,840 --> 00:25:26,120
