515
00:25:44,720 --> 00:25:45,520
They say you're

516
00:25:45,840 --> 00:25:47,640
an emotionless money-making machine.

517
00:25:49,880 --> 00:25:50,720
They have good judgment.

518
00:25:50,840 --> 00:25:51,720
Thank them for the compliment.

519
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:52,720
Anyway,

520
00:25:52,840 --> 00:25:53,520
from today on,

521
00:25:53,960 --> 00:25:55,240
keep hanging tightly

522
00:25:55,280 --> 00:25:56,520
onto the Zhou Xiaofeng tree for me.

523
00:25:56,520 --> 00:25:57,280
Hold on to him tightly.

524
00:25:57,600 --> 00:25:58,960
Launch a full attack on Dongli.

525
00:25:59,200 --> 00:26:00,320
Remember,

526
00:26:01,600 --> 00:26:02,320
from now on, Director Zhou

527
00:26:02,560 --> 00:26:03,920
will have your career

528
00:26:04,240 --> 00:26:05,120
by the throat.

529
00:26:05,120 --> 00:26:06,280
from now on, Director Zhou

530
00:26:06,520 --> 00:26:07,840
will have your career by the throat.

531
00:26:08,160 --> 00:26:09,200
So pay tribute when needed,

532
00:26:09,520 --> 00:26:10,520
kneel when needed.

533
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:13,200
Don't be too reserved.

534
00:26:13,440 --> 00:26:13,960
I know what I'm doing. Don't worry.

535
00:26:14,320 --> 00:26:15,840
Good.

536
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:17,240
