539
00:26:20,280 --> 00:26:21,720
And about the performance bonus...

540
00:26:29,560 --> 00:26:30,520
Everyone, everyone.

541
00:26:31,160 --> 00:26:32,560
Put your work aside for a moment.

542
00:26:33,840 --> 00:26:34,920
