546
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:42,400
and helped MyAmp

547
00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:44,520
make its first breakthrough at Dongli.

548
00:26:45,040 --> 00:26:45,840
She is our top contributor

549
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:46,760
So,

550
00:26:46,840 --> 00:26:47,520
I'll keep my promise.

551
00:26:47,960 --> 00:26:49,320
Starting today,

552
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:50,840
Dongli Heart Center

553
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:52,800
will officially be

554
00:26:53,040 --> 00:26:53,880
under Manager Ouyang's responsibility.

555
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:55,080
Her performance bonus level

556
00:26:55,600 --> 00:26:57,560
