557
00:26:58,200 --> 00:26:58,760
Applause.

558
00:27:02,080 --> 00:27:02,920
Keep it up.

559
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:03,840
Everyone has a chance.

560
00:27:04,320 --> 00:27:05,880
Thank you, President Qin.

561
00:27:07,120 --> 00:27:07,640
Ouyang,

562
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:08,920
