563
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:09,600
Thank you.

564
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:11,600
Ouyang really has something.

565
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:14,160
Female sales reps,

566
00:27:14,480 --> 00:27:15,480
