573
00:27:46,120 --> 00:27:46,600
Xiao Wu.

574
00:27:48,520 --> 00:27:49,840
Director Zhou, done with rounds?

575
00:27:50,440 --> 00:27:51,080
I've almost finished

576
00:27:51,120 --> 00:27:51,800
