607
00:28:32,600 --> 00:28:33,640
No problem.

608
00:28:33,800 --> 00:28:34,240
Okay, I won't disturb you.

609
00:29:00,800 --> 00:29:01,480
Thank you.

610
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:03,840
Oh my goodness.

611
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:10,960
Sorry.

612
