614
00:30:52,400 --> 00:30:53,800
Section Chief Wang, no need to see me off.

615
00:30:54,040 --> 00:30:54,640
Director Zhou, don't worry.

616
00:30:54,800 --> 00:30:56,120
This week,

617
00:30:56,200 --> 00:30:56,880
