637
00:31:23,880 --> 00:31:24,480
and have them come pick it up.

638
00:31:25,760 --> 00:31:26,520
Also,

639
00:31:26,840 --> 00:31:28,400
contact MyAmp

640
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:29,480
and settle the balloon payment.

641
00:31:37,080 --> 00:31:37,920
Okay.

642
00:31:41,280 --> 00:31:41,920
Manager Ouyang, thanks for waiting.

643
00:31:42,280 --> 00:31:43,520
Take a look.

644
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:45,240
If everything is fine, sign here.

645
00:31:45,280 --> 00:31:46,520
We'll follow the required process

646
00:31:47,040 --> 00:31:48,200
and transfer the money properly.

647
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:49,640
Actually, that's really unnecessary.

648
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:51,520
We can cover these costs.

649
00:31:51,760 --> 00:31:52,280
The director specifically instructed us.

650
00:31:52,280 --> 00:31:53,640
Manager Ouyang,

651
00:31:55,280 --> 00:31:56,520
