652
00:31:57,200 --> 00:31:57,840
Then I'll trouble you, Dr. Zhang.

653
00:31:59,160 --> 00:31:59,800
You're welcome.

654
00:31:59,800 --> 00:32:01,080
Once the payment is made,

655
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:05,520
I'll notify you immediately.

656
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:07,920
Dr. Zhang.

657
00:32:08,600 --> 00:32:09,400
This...

658
00:32:10,960 --> 00:32:11,720
