676
00:32:40,760 --> 00:32:41,760
That's great.

677
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:42,880
How about this?

678
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:44,280
Send me your wife's name too.

679
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:45,520
I'll try to get a personalized autograph.

680
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:47,440
A friend of mine

681
