682
00:32:48,560 --> 00:32:49,560
I'll see what I can do.

683
00:32:50,280 --> 00:32:50,840
Okay.

684
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:52,120
Then I won't stand on ceremony.

685
00:32:52,520 --> 00:32:53,080
Don't be polite.

686
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:53,720
I'll take it.

687
00:33:02,960 --> 00:33:03,560
Old Liu.

688
00:33:03,960 --> 00:33:04,520
Yes, yes.

689
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:05,560
I was the one who called you.

690
00:33:06,520 --> 00:33:08,120
Our approval process here

691
00:33:08,120 --> 00:33:08,840
