698
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:20,040
Careful.

699
00:33:22,280 --> 00:33:23,280
Watch that.

700
00:33:23,800 --> 00:33:24,520
Don't damage it.

701
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:26,560
Director Zhou.

702
00:33:26,920 --> 00:33:27,520
Thank you.

703
00:33:27,800 --> 00:33:28,880
You've really helped us when we needed it most.

704
00:33:29,200 --> 00:33:29,840
It's all old equipment.

705
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:30,840
