706
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:32,080
Of course it can.

707
00:33:32,440 --> 00:33:33,160
You know,

708
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:34,080
our hospital

709
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:35,200
