712
00:33:38,960 --> 00:33:39,640
This time,

713
00:33:40,560 --> 00:33:41,280
we'll have enough.

714
00:33:43,120 --> 00:33:44,160
Then I'll leave the equipment

715
00:33:44,200 --> 00:33:44,920
and the child to you.

716
00:33:45,320 --> 00:33:46,160
Don't worry.

717
00:33:49,840 --> 00:33:50,920
The baby will still need to stay

718
00:33:51,040 --> 00:33:52,040
