719
00:33:52,400 --> 00:33:53,560
Take care of yourself too.

720
00:33:54,600 --> 00:33:55,800
Don't worry, Dr. Fang.

721
00:33:56,120 --> 00:33:57,560
The rental place the hospital found for us

722
00:33:57,600 --> 00:33:58,520
is right beside here.

723
00:33:58,840 --> 00:33:59,920
It'll be convenient

724
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:01,120
