725
00:34:01,120 --> 00:34:02,120
and visiting the baby.

726
00:34:02,440 --> 00:34:02,840
Yes.

727
00:34:03,760 --> 00:34:05,320
If you need anything, tell us anytime.

728
00:34:05,960 --> 00:34:07,200
Okay. Thank you, Director Zhou.

729
00:34:07,840 --> 00:34:08,800
You've really helped us

730
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:09,560
so much.

731
00:34:09,840 --> 00:34:10,560
I don't even know

732
00:34:10,560 --> 00:34:11,640
