733
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:12,320
Yes.

734
00:34:12,640 --> 00:34:14,480
This is a gift she made herself.

735
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:16,040
It's for you.

736
00:34:16,200 --> 00:34:16,800
Yes.

737
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:18,880
Here, Director Zhou.

738
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:20,080
Thank you.

739
00:34:20,760 --> 00:34:22,240
Just a small blessing.

740
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:22,600
Thank you.

741
00:34:22,600 --> 00:34:23,640
I hope you stay safe

742
00:34:23,640 --> 00:34:24,520
and healthy.

743
00:34:24,560 --> 00:34:25,200
Thank you.

744
00:34:26,840 --> 00:34:27,480
Director Zhou.

745
00:34:27,960 --> 00:34:29,200
Please help me

746
00:34:29,280 --> 00:34:30,560
