747
00:34:33,520 --> 00:34:34,160
Thank you.

748
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:37,200
Please say goodbye to her for me, and thank her.

749
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:38,600
I will.

750
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:41,800
We truly thank you this time.

751
00:34:42,520 --> 00:34:43,160
Look.

752
00:34:43,560 --> 00:34:45,480
All right. Turn on the switch.

753
00:34:45,840 --> 00:34:46,320
You're going home now.

754
00:34:46,320 --> 00:34:47,320
Listen to Mom and Dad, okay?

755
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,200
Do you hear me?

756
00:34:48,840 --> 00:34:51,080
I'm going back to play soccer with them.

757
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:52,160
Soccer?

758
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:54,200
Director Zhou, let me tell you a secret.

759
00:34:54,720 --> 00:34:55,640
Next summer vacation,

760
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:57,160
I'm going to bring my classmates

761
00:34:57,320 --> 00:34:58,840
