762
00:34:59,600 --> 00:35:00,160
Great.

763
00:35:00,200 --> 00:35:01,160
You can be the tour guide.

764
00:35:02,120 --> 00:35:02,760
Director Zhou.

765
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:04,320
Director Zhou, Director Zhou.

766
00:35:05,200 --> 00:35:06,280
This is very important.

767
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:07,200
I almost forgot.

768
00:35:07,200 --> 00:35:07,640
This really isn't necessary.

769
00:35:07,640 --> 00:35:08,840
No, the old president

770
00:35:08,840 --> 00:35:09,640
told me again and again

771
00:35:09,840 --> 00:35:11,040
that I must personally

772
00:35:11,040 --> 00:35:11,960
