773
00:35:13,560 --> 00:35:14,800
Take a photo. Take a photo.

774
00:35:17,320 --> 00:35:18,200
Look here. Look here.

775
00:35:19,720 --> 00:35:21,320
Good. One more, one more.

776
00:35:49,840 --> 00:35:50,960
Are you free now?

777
00:35:58,120 --> 00:35:58,720
Once you become director,

778
00:35:58,840 --> 00:35:59,880
