779
00:36:00,520 --> 00:36:02,200
Either tea or coffee.

780
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:11,520
I saw Mom off that day.

781
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:15,400
I know.

782
00:36:20,120 --> 00:36:21,200
I apologized to her.

783
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:29,040
I know what I did

784
00:36:29,080 --> 00:36:30,120
was very wrong.

785
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:33,880
I hurt Mom.

786
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:35,880
I hurt you.

787
00:36:39,040 --> 00:36:40,320
I don't expect your forgiveness.

788
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,600
But I hope

789
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:45,440
you can at least understand me.

790
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:49,440
Two years ago,

791
00:36:50,560 --> 00:36:51,880
when I first arrived in Guizhou,

792
00:36:55,960 --> 00:36:57,200
Xuemie's eldest daughter

793
00:37:00,200 --> 00:37:01,480
died right in front of me.

794
00:37:23,200 --> 00:37:24,320
This patient's condition isn't good.

795
00:37:24,520 --> 00:37:25,320
Make way, make way.

796
00:37:25,400 --> 00:37:26,760
She was admitted to a lower-level hospital

797
00:37:26,800 --> 00:37:27,960
two days ago with viral gastroenteritis.

798
00:37:28,280 --> 00:37:29,280
An hour ago, she suddenly developed shortness of breath

799
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:30,120
and difficulty breathing,

800
00:37:30,320 --> 00:37:31,320
coughing pink frothy sputum.

801
00:37:31,440 --> 00:37:32,120
She also had ventricular fibrillation

802
00:37:32,120 --> 00:37:32,840
during transfer.

803
00:37:36,160 --> 00:37:36,760
Xiao He.

804
00:37:37,560 --> 00:37:38,760
Suspected fulminant myocarditis.

805
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:39,440
We need an urgent consult.

806
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:40,520
Contact ECMO,

807
00:37:40,520 --> 00:37:41,400
pediatrics, and cardiac surgery immediately.

808
00:37:41,400 --> 00:37:41,800
Okay.

809
00:37:42,080 --> 00:37:43,200
Also call hepatology, nephrology, and neurology.

810
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,080
Okay, got it.

811
00:37:50,720 --> 00:37:51,400
President Zhou.

812
00:37:52,040 --> 00:37:52,600
Director Ma.

813
00:37:52,640 --> 00:37:53,520
Has ECMO arrived?

814
00:37:53,520 --> 00:37:54,200
It's still on the way.

815
00:37:54,720 --> 00:37:55,600
Have you spoken with the family?

816
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:56,840
Is the informed consent signed?

817
00:37:57,200 --> 00:37:57,960
We've explained everything.

818
00:37:58,280 --> 00:37:59,440
The parents signed without hesitation.

819
00:37:59,640 --> 00:38:00,840
They said they'd sell everything they had

820
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:01,760
to save their child.

821
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:03,440
Excuse me, excuse me.

822
00:38:03,560 --> 00:38:04,160
Make way.

823
00:38:05,200 --> 00:38:05,800
President Zhou.

824
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:06,880
ECMO is here.

825
00:38:12,160 --> 00:38:12,800
Ten years old.

826
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:13,520
President Zhou.

827
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:15,040
We don't have

828
00:38:15,080 --> 00:38:16,080
tubing suitable for a child.

829
00:38:16,600 --> 00:38:17,200
What?

830
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:20,880
This...

831
00:38:22,720 --> 00:38:23,640
I'm sorry, this is

832
00:38:23,640 --> 00:38:24,480
really urgent.

833
00:38:24,960 --> 00:38:26,040
I remember your company also represents

834
00:38:26,040 --> 00:38:26,600
ECMO, right?

835
00:38:27,400 --> 00:38:28,240
Do you know any suppliers

836
00:38:28,280 --> 00:38:29,040
in Guizhou?

837
00:38:29,640 --> 00:38:30,400
I need

838
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:31,560
tubing for a ten-year-old child.

839
00:38:32,200 --> 00:38:33,840
Fulminant myocarditis. She can't be transferred.

840
00:38:34,200 --> 00:38:35,080
Okay, okay. Thank you.

841
00:38:35,160 --> 00:38:35,560
Sorry to trouble you.

842
00:38:38,320 --> 00:38:38,840
Hello?

843
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:39,280
Director.

844
00:38:39,440 --> 00:38:40,560
I've prepared the tubing here.

845
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:41,840
I checked the fastest logistics.

846
00:38:42,080 --> 00:38:42,640
It will reach you

847
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:43,720
around noon tomorrow.

848
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:46,520
All right. I understand.

849
00:38:48,080 --> 00:38:48,720
Nini.

850
00:38:49,040 --> 00:38:49,720
Nini.

851
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:51,240
Why are you only back now?

852
00:38:52,640 --> 00:38:53,240
My child.

853
00:38:53,240 --> 00:38:54,920
What's going on? What's wrong with Nini?

854
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:55,720
We're doing everything we can to save her.

855
00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:57,240
Please save my daughter.

856
00:38:57,320 --> 00:38:58,200
I'm begging you.

857
00:38:58,280 --> 00:38:59,760
No matter what, please save her.

858
00:39:00,080 --> 00:39:00,760
Please, doctor.

859
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:01,280
President Zhou.

860
00:39:02,720 --> 00:39:03,880
That pediatric tubing

861
00:39:04,960 --> 00:39:06,280
arrived three hours later.

862
00:39:09,040 --> 00:39:10,120
But it was already too late.

863
00:39:12,520 --> 00:39:13,560
If ECMO

864
00:39:13,560 --> 00:39:14,960
had arrived a little sooner,

865
00:39:15,520 --> 00:39:17,080
or if the primary hospital doctors

866
00:39:18,400 --> 00:39:19,800
had made the judgment earlier,

867
00:39:22,520 --> 00:39:23,720
the result

868
00:39:32,480 --> 00:39:33,280
would have been different.

869
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:36,760
At Dongli,

870
00:39:36,840 --> 00:39:38,520
we've become used to

871
00:39:39,120 --> 00:39:39,880
having a strong team behind us.

872
00:39:40,720 --> 00:39:41,840
We have people when we need them,

873
00:39:43,600 --> 00:39:45,200
equipment when we need it.

874
00:39:45,520 --> 00:39:46,600
But it's different in primary hospitals.

875
00:39:52,520 --> 00:39:53,240
They lack everything.

876
00:39:53,240 --> 00:39:54,200
So since I was appointed

877
00:39:55,200 --> 00:39:56,560
vice president there,

878
00:39:56,760 --> 00:39:58,040
I tried every possible way to get staff,

879
00:39:58,640 --> 00:39:59,400
get equipment, and make reforms.

880
00:39:59,440 --> 00:40:00,720
And I did manage

881
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:02,840
to make some changes.

882
00:40:03,040 --> 00:40:03,880
I truly saw

883
00:40:04,240 --> 00:40:04,960
many patients

884
00:40:04,960 --> 00:40:06,760
no longer having to run back and forth

885
00:40:09,320 --> 00:40:10,720
between the hospital and the mountains.

886
00:40:11,600 --> 00:40:12,720
